@startuml ManagerLifecycleStateMachine
title Manager Lifecycle State Machine

[*] --> Idle: (initial C++ state)

' Startup paths
Idle --> Initializing: run()
Initializing --> StartingModules: handle_start_modules() \n[default or no --into-idle]
Initializing --> Idle: run() \n[--into-idle flag]

' Normal running
StartingModules --> Running: handle_start_modules() \n[all modules ready + \nno shutdown in progress]

' Graceful shutdown paths
Running --> ShutdownRequested: handle_initiate_graceful_shutdown() \n[SIGINT/SIGTERM or \nmodule crash]
StartingModules --> ShutdownRequested: handle_initiate_graceful_shutdown()

ShutdownRequested --> ForceTerminating: handle_shutdown_timeout() \n[>5s without all \nmodules exiting]

CrashShutdownInProgress --> ForceTerminating: handle_shutdown_timeout() \n[>5s timeout]

ForceTerminating --> ShutdownFinalizing: handle_shutdown_timeout() \n[>5s grace timeout \nfor SIGKILL]

' Crash detection & handling
Running --> CrashShutdownInProgress: handle_child_exit() \n[unexpected module exit \nduring Running]
StartingModules --> CrashShutdownInProgress: handle_child_exit() \n[unexpected module exit \nduring StartingModules]

' Shutdown finalization -> Idle (no SIGINT)
ShutdownRequested --> ShutdownFinalizing: advance_lifecycle_state_if_ready() \n[all module_handles_ \nempty]
CrashShutdownInProgress --> ShutdownFinalizing: advance_lifecycle_state_if_ready() \n[all module_handles_ \nempty]
RestartRequested --> ShutdownFinalizing: advance_lifecycle_state_if_ready() \n[all module_handles_ \nempty]

ShutdownFinalizing --> StartingModules: handle_restart_modules_after_shutdown() \n[crash recovery + \nattempts remaining]

ShutdownFinalizing --> Idle: handle_finish_crash_recovery() \n[crash recovery + \nattempts exhausted]
ShutdownFinalizing --> Idle: handle_finish_normal_shutdown() \n[normal shutdown, \nno SIGINT received]

' Restart from Idle
Idle --> StartingModules: handle_restart_modules_after_shutdown() \n[config service \nstart callback]

' Admin restart
Running --> RestartRequested: handle_controller_ipc_poll() \n[restart request \nfrom LifecycleAPI]

' Exit paths
ShutdownFinalizing --> Exiting: handle_finish_normal_shutdown() \n[normal shutdown + \nSIGINT received]
ShutdownFinalizing --> Exiting: handle_shutdown_timeout() \n[force-kill \nescalation]

Idle --> ShutdownRequested: handle_signal() \n[SIGINT/SIGTERM \nwhile in Idle]
Idle --> Exiting: handle_signal() \n[second SIGINT \n(abort)]

Exiting --> [*]: run() exit

note right of Idle
  Manager alive, modules down
  Can restart via API or SIGINT to exit
end note

note right of Running
  All modules started and ready
  Can handle graceful shutdown or restarts
end note

note right of ShutdownRequested
  Published MQTT shutdown topic
  Waiting for modules to exit
end note

note right of CrashShutdownInProgress
  Unexpected module exit detected
  Draining remaining modules
end note

note right of ForceTerminating
  Graceful timeout expired
  Force-killing remaining modules
end note

note right of ShutdownFinalizing
  All modules exited
  Deciding: restart, idle, or exit
end note

@enduml
